<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> jung <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Hutt
                        fürbracht, wie er mit <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Görg
                                <expan>Aichperg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>zu Seldnaw</add> etlich sache zu handeln hab,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er sein <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        yecz zu im schik; <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr gnade mit fleisz,
                        derselben <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
                        sachen umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ewr
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <pb facs="#facs_414" id="206r"/>guten willen
                        zu beweisen. Als etc. Das wellen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. <lb/>Andre
                                <expan>Erlisperg<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Passaw,
                            <lb/><expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Heymram Nothaft, <add>verweser</add> in
                                <expan>Nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan>peyrn
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>. </ab>
